        "created_at": "2024-05-02T05:48:01.113Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m over here right now and have spent a lot more time walking around vineyards than I have in the past. It occurred to me that there are no bathroom facilities basically anywhere in or around vineyards. I realize most vineyards there are carved up into many sections and having innumerable mobile bathrooms would be unsustainable. Still, if you\u2019re in the middle of Le Charlemagne on a terribly steep slope and the second cup of morning coffee is kicking in\u2026</p>\n<p>Realize it\u2019s not the most awesome of topics but wondered what the story is and if anyone knew.</p>",
